'''Bodden Town''' is a district of the island of [[Grand Cayman]] in the [[Cayman Islands]]. It takes its name from [[Bodden Town (village)|the village of Bodden Town]], which is located on the south shore of the island in the central portion of the district. Other communities in the district of Bodden Town are [[Savannah, Cayman Islands|Savannah]] and [[Newlands, Grand Cayman|Newlands]], both in the western portion of the district.

