{{Politics of Congo (Brazzaville)}} The [[Departments of the Republic of the Congo]] are divided into 86 districts and 6 [[Communes of the Republic of the Congo|communes]]. Note the departments of [[Brazzaville]] and [[Pointe-Noire]] are made of 1 commune each, then divided in urban districts (''arrondissements'').
